HR Analyst cần lương trung vị theo phòng ban thay vì trung bình để loại bỏ ảnh hưởng outlier (giám đốc, intern).

Yêu cầu: trả về dept, median_salary (xử lý đúng cả N lẻ và N chẵn) — sắp xếp dept tăng dần
```sql
WITH rnk_in_salary AS (
    SELECT
        dept,
        salary,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY dept
            ORDER BY salary
        ) AS rnk,
        COUNT(*) OVER (
            PARTITION BY dept
        ) AS cnt
    FROM employees
)
SELECT
    dept,
    AVG(salary * 1.0) AS median_salary
FROM rnk_in_salary
WHERE rnk IN (
    (cnt + 1) / 2,
    (cnt + 2) / 2
)
GROUP BY dept
ORDER BY dept;
```
